sentences.english: The glycemic index ranks foods based on how much they raise blood sugar.

sentences.english: If pregnant, take an iron supplement, as recommended by an obstetrician or other health care provider.

sentences.english: Results Food-poisoning accidents happen more frequently in the third quarter.

sentences.english: Sensing food, a roach peers into a two-foot-tall pitcher plant.

sentences.english: Reduce edible salt bloats, smoke, barbecue food.

sentences.english: These camp robbers hae become habituated to campers as a food source.
